(17) Spawning site recommendations: On April 25th, 1999, a slide occurred in Nomash Valley moving large amounts of debris into Nomash River, a tributary of the Zeballos River. The slide put enough sedimentation into the Zeballos River system to colour the Zeballos Inlet down as far as Centre Island. This slide will impact the 1998 brood offsprings.
